To accommodate students who don't have credit cards, the best strategy is to offer "Cardless" payment methods. In South Africa, students prefer Vouchers and Instant EFT (banking without a card).
Here is the breakdown of the best options for your "Optional Donation" button:
1. The Winner for Vouchers: 1Voucher / OTT Voucher
Many students carry cash or have money in "digital wallets" rather than on a bank card.
 * How it works: A student buys a "1Voucher" or "OTT Voucher" at a Spaza shop, Flash vendor, Pep, or Shoprite (just like airtime). They enter the PIN on your site.
 * Why it‚Äôs best: It is the most "inclusive" method. If a student has R10 cash, they can support you.
 * How to get it: You don't talk to the shops. You sign up for a payment gateway like Netcash or Adumo Online. They provide the code to put a "Pay with Voucher" button on your site.
2. The Winner for EFT: Capitec Pay / Ozow
Most students in SA bank with Capitec or use TymeBank. They often don't have their physical cards on them, or they find entering card digits annoying.
 * How it works: * Capitec Pay: The student just enters their phone number. They get a "pop-up" on their banking app to click "Approve."
   * Ozow / Instant EFT: They log in with their banking details once and approve the R5 or R10 payment.
 * Why it‚Äôs best: It‚Äôs extremely fast and feels "high-tech" and safe.
 * How to get it: Sign up for Ozow or PayFast. They both support these "Instant EFT" methods.
3. The "All-in-One" Solution: PayFast
If you don't want to sign up for five different things, PayFast is your best bet because they bundle almost everything together.
 * Vouchers: They support SCode (where the student gets a barcode, goes to a store, and pays cash).
 * EFT: They support Instant EFT for all major SA banks.
 * Cards: They still support normal debit cards for those who have them.
Comparison for a "R10 Donation"
| Method | Ease for Student | Best Feature | Fees (Approx) |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1Voucher | 10/10 | Use Cash from Spaza | ~3% - 5% |
| Capitec Pay | 10/10 | No card digits needed | ~R1.00 - R2.00 |
| Instant EFT | 8/10 | Direct from Bank | ~R2.00 flat |
| Ozow.ME | 9/10 | QR Code / Link | R0.00 |
Summary Recommendation:
 * For Professionalism: Use PayFast or Netcash. This gives you one button that covers Vouchers, EFT, and Cards.
 * For Maximum Profit: Use Ozow.ME. Since it has zero fees for you, a R5 donation stays a R5 donation.
